tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE songs (
  song_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  song_name VARCHAR(255),
  artist_name VARCHAR(255),
  instrument_used VARCHAR(100)
)
CREATE TABLE Song (song_id INT PRIMARY KEY, song_name VARCHAR(255), artist_name VARCHAR(255), instrument_used VARCHAR(255));
CREATE TABLE Playlist (playlist_id INT PRIMARY KEY, playlist_name VARCHAR(255), song_id INT, FOREIGN KEY(song_id) REFERENCES Song(song_id));

CREATE TABLE songs (song_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  song_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
  artist VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
  instrument_used VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL);

CREATE TABLE instruments (instrument_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  instrument_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL);

CREATE TABLE song_instruments (song_id UUID,
  instrument_id UUID,
  FOREIGN KEY (song_id) REFERENCES songs(song_id),
  FOREIGN KEY (instrument_id) REFERENCES instruments(instrument_id));

CREATE TABLE playlists (playlist_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  playlist_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL);
